com.camerontec.catalys.core.fixvalidation.datatype

Class AbstractDateValidator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.camerontec.catalys.core.fixvalidation.datatype.AbstractDateValidator
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    UTCDateOnlyValidator, UTCTimeStampValidator

    public abstract class AbstractDateValidator
extends Object
    Provides methods for validating date strings without a regex. This is much faster, > 10x, than the regex approach which is overkill for simple fixed date formats. Note none of these methods check the length of the input string, callers should do that before calling these methods.
